            <pb facs="#IMG.1" n="1"/>
            <dateline>28 Oct. 00 15 Rawlinson Rd, Oxford</dateline>
            <p>I am much obliged to you for sending me your <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
Klassifikation der Rom. Mund</hi>.<note n="1" place="foot" type="editorial">
Schuchardt (1900). <bibl>
                     <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.bibliography#BIBL.309">
                        <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">Über die Klassifikation der romanischen Mundarten. Probevorlesung gehalten zu Leipzig am 30. April 1870</hi>
                     </ref>
                  </bibl>.</note> I have read it with great interest. It is an important historical document showing how much you were in advance of your contemporaries, &amp; how long ago you had articulated the ‘new views’.</p>
            <closer>
               <signed>
                  <persName ref="[authorityLink]">H. Sweet</persName>
               </signed>
            </closer>
            <pb facs="#IMG.2" n="2"/>
         </div>
